works.description:
If someone searches for Serres Greece he  
sees the map of Serres.
Serres is a city of Northern Greece where our Technological and Educational  
Institute is located.
At the place of our location someone put in Greek the following  
sign "ΠΑΡΑΠΡΟΙΟΝΤΑ ΣΕΡΡΩΝ ΕΠΕ" which is offensive and demeaning for our  
institution.
We kindly request you to remove the sign and replace it with our name: "ΤΕΙ  
ΣΕΡΡΩΝ".
Thanks in advance.
Best regards.
